title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 21 2022
description:
Clay and Buck show comes from WSFX in Ft. Myers, with Buck remote in quarantine. Trump says DeSantis story is totally fake news. Ukraine fiasco: Clean up on Aisle Biden. Senator Rand Paul joins Clay and Buck to talk about his quest to end covid mandates, Omicron, and the future of Dr. Fauci. C&B on the '90s and men in scarves. Caller praises Dr. Rand Paul.
